    "title": "Assistant Store Manager - Starbucks India - Apply Now",
    "description": "Starbucks India is actively seeking a talented and motivated Assistant Store Manager to join our dynamic team in Jaipur. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Starbucks India:\nStarbucks India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jaipur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Starbucks India!",
